Class ComplexNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.hw02.ComplexNumber

  • public class ComplexNumber
extends java.lang.Object
    Class ComplexNumber represents an unmodifiable complex number. Both real and imaginary parts are double numbers.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Toni Martinčić
